{"tid":348784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求助 搭錯車點算 入黎笑下我","createTime":"2017-08-06T04:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T11:23:23.000Z","uid":2880,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"533dd0a8f1bb2aaa96489ca5adfda9b875a6182f","tid":348784,"uid":2880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:29:31.000Z","msg":"琴晚通宵完 咁剛剛諗住搭車翻沙田（287x）<br />\n<br />\n點知瞌下瞌下又掛住睇電話<br />\n<br />\n黎遠見到有287x就心諗上得啦<br />\n<br />\n原來有部268x爬咗頭<br />\n<br />\n我又唔知頭唔知路上左車<br />\n<br />\n仲要一上車就訓（平時落總站）<br />\n<br />\n一訓醒去撚咗洪水橋<br />\n<br />\n我當堂呆撚咗<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知道咩方法翻沙田最快（沙角邨個頭）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cc9cd64f8990a4b13a4e9cf6d3d608f5b81dfc","tid":348784,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:30:40.000Z","msg":"標準答案 的士"},{"pid":"c072ec3352952e846444892047c7eb00959ba2d1","tid":348784,"uid":2880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標準答案 的士</blockquote><br />\n毒撚好窮"},{"pid":"4fb4648c6b5b2f01ca1ff569ec96d440c8b325ca","tid":348784,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"269D 返到沙田市中心<br />\n或者<br />\n269D 城隧轉 47X"},{"pid":"03680a68465335a56871565b0b91129fb9a977c1","tid":348784,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>269D 返到沙田市中心<br />\n或者<br />\n269D 城隧轉 47X</blockquote><br />\n唔想行就求其上一部大欖隧道既車去到再轉<br />\n有轉乘優惠"},{"pid":"34e611fd2062f06275cc467e926eb1353e7f85ce","tid":348784,"uid":85819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4f67ac2960baf647e31b37c623897a5b25cfac8","tid":348784,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>269D 返到沙田市中心<br />\n或